Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
With Spec 1 fully committed, planning is being finalised for two brand new industrial units available for lease being located within Nexus North Industrial Estate. Individual tenancies or can be combined for larger floorplan. To be completed to the highest quality incorporating sustainable design and features. Get in early to incorporate specific design features to suit your operational requirements.

https://www.nexusnorth.com.au/

Unit 1: 2,371 sqm* Warehouse + 160sqm* single storey office (plus outdoor area)
Unit 2: 2,369 sqm* Warehouse + 160sqm* single storey office (plus outdoor area)

** Can be combined for 4,740sqm Warehouse plus offices

- Separate car parking for both units and ample room for B-Double access and turnaround
- Flexible floorplans
- High clearance warehouses
- Automatic roller shutter doors
- Airconditioned corporate office facilities
- LED high bay lighting
- High voltage power
- Hardstand/truck manoeuvring areas
- Fully landscaped with security fencing

Nexus North Industrial Estate is currently being developed by ILP and promotes a gateway location to major transport routes including Main North Road, Salisbury Highway and North-South Connector.

The Estate is surrounded by prominent brands including Bridgestone, Coca-Cola, Lion, Border Express & Bickfords Group.

Detailed Specifications and plans are available by request.

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: SPEC 2 COMING SOON! - COMPLETION DUE QTR 1 2022
